race.description: Cwnet P/L Hcp (C2) - Heat Of The Rising Star
race.comment: Toughest race of the day with plenty of chances. IRISH JIG (5) opened his prep with a sharp win at Kembla, then no match for the progressive The Three Hundred when sixth over 1200m at Wyong in fast time. Gets a better set-up today with the 3kg claim and the blinkers stay on. Ready to bounce back. LETHAL LOVE (10) rewarded for her consistency when getting off the mark at start six to salute over 1300m at Hawkesbury. Well placed again and expected to go close. MARVEL MAN (1) tough gelding racing in career best form. Nailed late with the 60kg when second over 1100m at Mudgee in C3 grade. The 3kg claim keeps him in the mix. ROMANTIC LOVE (4) relished the rise in trip when a gritty on-pace winner over 1200m at Narromine. Place best at this level.
